title: The Big Suey: Becky Hammon
description:
The crew discusses Erling Haaland's excellence, LeBron's public plea to own a team in Las Vegas, and whether or not we should even be talking about Tom Brady's potential divorce. Then, 2022 WNBA Champion and Coach of the Year Becky Hammon joins the show.
